  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p>Vicuna is a chat assistant model. It includes 3 different variants in 3 different sizes. v1.3 is trained by fine-tuning Llama and has a context size of 2048 tokens. v1.5 is trained by fine-tuning Llama 2 and has a context size of 2048 tokens. v1.5-16k is trained by fine-tuning Llama 2 and has a context size of 16k tokens. All three variants are trained using conversations collected from ShareGPT.</p>\n\n<h2>Example prompts</h2>\n\n<pre><code>What is the meaning of life? Explain it in 5 paragraphs.\n</code></pre>\n\n<h2>References</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/lmsys\" rel=\"nofollow\">HuggingFace</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
